<Location>//Fortnite/Main/Engine/Source/ThirdParty/Catch2/ and all streams in the P4 stream tree and robomerge graph that include this folder.</Location>
<Function>A modern C++ test library, last version approved by TPS was 3.4.0. It's never packaged with Shipping configuration builds.
Users with source code access can build non-shipping configurations that will include the Catch2 library and the source code will be included with the source code of the engine for all types of users.
Licensees that build from github mirrored code also have access: https://github.com/EpicGames/UnrealEngine/tree/release/Engine/Source/ThirdParty/Catch2
</Function>
